<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.210139>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Aromobates zippeli sp. nov. (A) Lateral view of subadult paratopotype female CVULA 8341. (B) Ventral view of same specimen in A. (C) two uncollected specimens, showing variation in pattern. Photos by CBA." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/210139/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.210133>
    dc:description "FIGURE 3. Collection localities including type localities of Aromobates (squares) along the Cordillera de Mérida, Serranía de Perijá, and northern Eastern Cordillera of Colombia. Several species might be sympatric and syntopic." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/210133/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

